  "text": "Furthermore, we collected demographic information with a questionnaire before the experiment and measured the participants' sense of presence with the Slater-Usoh-Steed (SUS) questionnaire [CITATION_1] , as well as simulator sickness with the Kennedy-Lane SSQ [CITATION_2] before and after the experiment. The total time per participant including pre-questionnaires, instructions, training, experiment, breaks, and debriefing was 1 hour. Participants were immersed in the VE for about 45 minutes.",
